The molecular formula for (5R)-5-(1,3-thiazol-4-yl)-1,4-oxazepane is C10H13N2OS, which consists of 10 carbon atoms (C), 13 hydrogen atoms (H), 2 nitrogen atoms (N), 1 oxygen atom (O), and 1 sulfur atom (S).

Therefore, the total number of atoms in (5R)-5-(1,3-thiazol-4-yl)-1,4-oxazepane is:
10 (C) + 13 (H) + 2 (N) + 1 (O) + 1 (S) = 27 atoms

Therefore, there are 27 atoms in (5R)-5-(1,3-thiazol-4-yl)-1,4-oxazepane.
